  "decoyDialogTitle": "Decoy vault",
  "decoySetupBody": "A decoy vault is a second, fully separate vault unlocked with a different password.\n\nUse case: if someone forces you to open Pass Tech (border, assault, control), you give the decoy password. The app then shows a fake vault — it is cryptographically impossible to prove the real one exists.\n\nKeep in mind:\n• The decoy password must differ from the real one\n• Fill the decoy with a few credible entries\n• You cannot enable biometrics on the decoy",
